                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/405" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0060</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9812 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北周黑鸭食品公司：为走向全国做准备</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hubei Zhouheiya : from Local to Nation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">田志龙，龙晓枫等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖北周黑鸭食品公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">26 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周黑鸭；扩张；战略管理；2011百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhouheiya; Expansion; Strategic Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010年，湖北周黑鸭食品有限公司进入快速发展阶段。对于发展战略和实现方式，公司创始人周富裕面临一系列问题需要回答：在主要竞争对手已经在全国布局的情况下，周黑鸭需要迅速扩张到全国吗？扩张是坚持采用直营的方式还是转而采用加盟的方式？公司的产品和服务结构是否需要调整？在扩张中是否因地制宜改变口味，改变门店风格以及提供餐馆和饮料服务？同行业竞争对手的扩张必然加剧上游资源的争夺，因此是否需要建立自己的上游供应链？扩张带来的资金压力如何解决？引入战略投资者还是财务投资者，或者上市？这项工作如何准备？针对这些问题，周富裕自己有很多想法，他的管理团队也提出了各种建议，这些有待他做出决定。本案例适用于《战略管理》和《创业》等课程，它给学生提供了一个了解传统行业的创业型企业成长过程以及分析公司发展过程中面临的市场扩张等战略决策问题的机会。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Hubei Zhouheiya steps into a fast development stage in 2010.In terms of development strategy and implementation, Zhou Fuyu, the founder of Zhouheiya, encounters a number of problems:1)Should Zhouheiya expand all over the country ,under the circumstance that the main competitors have occupied most of the market, maintaining regular chain or changing to franchisee? 2) Is it necessary to modify the structure of products and service, whether adjusting the taste and store style to the new market and catering for the guests or not? 3) Should the company build upstream supply chain, considering fierce competition for the supplied resources among the rivals? 4) How can Zhou Fuyu overcome the problem of funds, bringing in strategic investors or financial investors ,or going public? In the case, Zhou Fuyu has a lot of ideas , his top management team also comes up with all kinds of proposals, but it is Zhou Fuyu that should make a decision finally. The case is applied for curricula such as Strategic Management and Entrepreneurship, offering a good opportunity for students to understand an entrepreneurial enterprise’ s development stage in a traditional industry and imitate to make strategic decisions on market expansion as a chairman.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《创业》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略管理导论；外部环境分析与内部条件分析；企业成长战略及其实施措施；创业成长的积累与条件；扩张发展基于的可复制能力；成长战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010-10</td>
                            </tr>
